<topic id="workflow-with-bpmn">
   <title>Authoring business processes with BPMN</title>
   <body>
      <p>This section lists the newly supported Business Process Model And Notation (BPMN) elements in the technology preview and describes how to use them in the Canvas workflow editor.</p>
      <section id="_supported_bpmn_process_elements">
         <title>Supported BPMN process elements</title>
